INSERT INTO `product_details` VALUES (38, 710, '件', '<div class=\"content_tpl\"><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t286/225/1384614246/187871/c0905ac3/5437c039N095ef4f1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-1\" name=\"detail-tag-id-1\" text=\"产品功能\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品功能</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Product Function</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t292/26/1372369023/183117/1b7a358/5437c01cNcc9187a1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">六重色彩处理引擎技术是TCL独家科技，无论是动态画面还是静态画面，都令其有非常出色的色彩和清晰度。很好地保证了快速运动画面的稳定、流畅、无卡顿，并且色彩饱和度高、锐度高，从而使图像平面上的细节对比度也更高，看起来更清楚更鲜艳。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t328/180/1353944288/138925/6f3960b2/5437c05dNb44c9800.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">TCL独有自然光技术是业内健康、环保、节能的科技典范，获得国家知识产权局颁发的中国专利金奖（专利号：ZL200710306638.8）。自然光技术将人造光线偏振光转化成自然光圆偏振光，不但能保护视力，同时功耗节能54%，配合电视5000:1的静态对比度，以及50000:1的动态对比度，让画面层次感更丰富。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t331/237/1362084929/111492/22ba379e/5437c067Nde2dca6d.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">在音箱的设计上，真正从消费者的诉求出发，采用了TCL鹦鹉螺音响系统，仿生学设计，采用了两个超薄防振重低音音箱单元配置，电源独立四驱动设计，以保证音箱的发声效果。并应用了TCL隐形磁悬浮专利技术和气悬浮处理技术，让声音亮丽清脆，立体饱满，精巧纤薄的设计，精密的防共振单元，让机体在音效表现上也相当出众。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t334/286/1375920023/103243/c527104a/5437c08dN8373cf9a.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">现在，只需把你喜欢的多媒体文件（电影/音乐/图片）拷贝到U盘/移动硬盘后，插上电视的USB接口就可以轻松在电视大屏上与朋友、家人一起体验，无需使用电脑或其他设备。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t334/313/1361404434/133426/420d8538/5437c0a0N09deb5ee.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-11\" name=\"detail-tag-id-11\" text=\"产品展示\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品展示</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Products Exhibition</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t349/50/1365479967/65477/7e72759a/5437c0c9N7f464d59.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t295/333/1352295982/54523/b4a2f055/5437c0cfN6220a725.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t322/109/1366155574/61060/9055be82/5437c0d8N97e1eb37.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t352/296/1367124873/38113/bcac3546/5437c0dcNa9f1c9f3.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t304/346/1331572227/58844/e436cc58/5437c0e1Nf3d31fcd.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-17\" name=\"detail-tag-id-17\" text=\"品牌介绍\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>品牌介绍</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Brand Introduction</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t220/283/2088290851/26436/8a01866/5406ef9fN43c1b493.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t211/232/1748838396/150325/deede591/53fda647Nc147d57b.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><