状和手写内容即时变成完美的图形和数字文本。全新升级的S Note如您所愿，打造精彩生活。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g14/M02/11/05/rBEhV1I6zKsIAAAAAAB1ZSx4iw0AADWgwF7wYcAAHV9919.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">随笔输入</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:24px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">手写替代键盘输入</span><br />GALAXY Note3 具备进一步升级更加先进的手写识别技术，打破了之前只有<br />S Note功能才可进行手写识别的限制。现在，无论是日历、闹钟，还是发短信、拨打电话都可通过手写识别实现。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g13/M06/0C/0C/rBEhUlI6zNkIAAAAAACB5vkZcP0AADT7gGd19sAAIH-086.jpg\" /></span></div></div></div>', 52, '2018-05-30 14:58:27', '2018-05-30 14:58:27');
